簽果條辛丑條約 一戰果時民國繼續還<br />\n仲要還到1938年因爲打二戰窮到pk<br />\n去求條約國唔追辛丑賠款先可以停<br />\n既然中共自稱滿清正統承繼人<br />\n呢張債券自然本利點都要還<br />\n唔還既佢講乜差野要用南京條約去收番香港<br />\n而且美國政府係未同中共追還錢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpU2AG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpU2AG.jpg&h=45a46f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">緊係侵侵啦！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/special3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"67187df530491b3c309338b6cd6f94fecc1c4cc9","tid":1571294,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c8a28b224c362c11a2dfb9e8e84d63e18e4b18d","tid":1571294,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed5bb86f6cba09aa52d1d3194cdfbf9a433bdb21","tid":1571294,"uid":18577,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"去天后啦！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:40:33.000Z","msg":"一路退就一路封咁仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:41:22.000Z","msg":"但都要天后方向架啦"},{"pid":"53c6bca4abf02af98434fdc470f66f2eb6ff7238","tid":1571294,"uid":21447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:41:55.000Z","msg":"天后未封但要快"},{"pid":"32d05e1edeb67cae1d758f44e8dac7a35e3b5b1a","tid":1571294,"uid":272202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:42:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4413dc05eea3174aeef28c79d9dc387844916d38","tid":1571294,"uid":69960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:42:40.000Z","msg":"去坐船走"},{"pid":"53310fd340904c0017a508b167c3f8b2ca7340c0","tid":1571294,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T11:43:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1772018e665f0bbd73f5856424c7c1dc9a0c0e91","tid":1571294,"uid":18577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53c6bca4abf02af984